---
---
<section id="difference" class="px-6 py-20 md:py-28 border-t border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)]">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
		<p class="text-[#EC4899] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-center">The blind spot</p>
		<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white text-center mt-3 tracking-tight leading-tight">
			Google traffic is shrinking.<br class="hidden md:block"/>AI traffic converts 5&times; better.
		</h2>
		<p class="text-[#A1A1AA] text-base md:text-lg text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4 leading-relaxed">
			Gartner predicts a 50% decline in organic search traffic by 2028. The traffic is moving to AI answers — and AI answers cite sites optimized for extraction, not just ranking.
		</p>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5 mt-14">

			<!-- Without AEOrank -->
			<div class="feat-card feat-card--bad animate-slide-left">
				<div class="feat-card__rule feat-card__rule--bad"></div>
				<div class="feat-card__inner">
					<div class="feat-card__header">
						<span class="feat-badge feat-badge--bad">
							<svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
						</span>
						<span class="feat-label feat-label--bad">Without AEOrank</span>
					</div>
					<ul class="feat-list">
						<li class="feat-item">
							<span class="feat-icon feat-icon--bad">
								<svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
							</span>
							<span>Invisible to ChatGPT, Perplexity, Claude — competitors get cited instead</span>
						</li>
						<li class="feat-item">
							<span class="feat-icon feat-icon--bad">
								<svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
							</span>
							<span>No llms.txt, no ai.txt — AI crawlers have zero context about your site</span>
						</li>
						<li class="feat-item">
							<span class="feat-icon feat-icon--bad">
								<svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
							</span>
							<span>GPTBot and ClaudeBot blocked by default in most hosting configs</span>
						</li>
						<li class="feat-item">
							<span class="feat-icon feat-icon--bad">
								<svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
							</span>
							<span>Content structured for Google snippets, not AI extraction</span>
						</li>
						<li class="feat-item">
							<span class="feat-icon feat-icon--bad">
								<svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
							</span>
							<span>No way to measure, track, or prevent AI visibility regressions</span>
						</li>
						<li class="feat-item">
							<span class="feat-icon feat-icon--bad">
								<svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
							</span>
							<span>Paying $129+/mo for a dashboard that only monitors — doesn't fix</span>
						</li>
						<li class="feat-item">
							<span class="feat-icon feat-icon--bad">
								<svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
							</span>
							<span>No way to show clients or stakeholders how your brand compares in AI answers</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- With AEOrank -->
			<div class="feat-card feat-card--good animate-slide-right">
				<div class="feat-card__rule feat-card__rule--good"></div>
				<div class="feat-card__inner">
					<div class="feat-card__header">
						<span class="feat-badge feat-badge--good">
							<svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
						</span>
						<span class="feat-label feat-label--good">With AEOrank</span>
					</div>
					<ul class="feat-list">
						<li class="feat-item">
							<span class="feat-icon feat-icon--good">
								<svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
							</span>
							<span>Score 0–100 across 36 criteria — know exactly where you stand</span>
						</li>
						<li class="feat-item">
							<span class="feat-icon feat-icon--good">
								<svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
							</span>
							<span>9 AI-readable files auto-generated — llms.txt, ai.txt, schema.json, more</span>
						</li>
						<li class="feat-item">
							<span class="feat-icon feat-icon--good">
								<svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
							</span>
							<span>AI crawler access configured correctly — every engine, every bot</span>
						</li>
						<li class="feat-item">
							<span class="feat-icon feat-icon--good">
								<svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
							</span>
							<span>Content analyzed for AI extractability — not just SEO, but AEO</span>
						</li>
						<li class="feat-item">
							<span class="feat-icon feat-icon--good">
								<svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
							</span>
							<span>PR checks catch regressions before deploy — scores on every commit</span>
						</li>
						<li class="feat-item">
							<span class="feat-icon feat-icon--good">
								<svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
							</span>
							<span>Free, open source, self-hostable — no vendor, no lock-in, no bill</span>
						</li>
						<li class="feat-item">
							<span class="feat-icon feat-icon--good">
								<svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
							</span>
							<span>Shareable score report — show clients, stakeholders, or your board exactly where you stand</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	/* ── Card shell ── */
	.feat-card {
		position: relative;
		border-radius: 14px;
		overflow: hidden;
		transition: transform 0.22s ease, box-shadow 0.22s ease;
	}
	.feat-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}
	.feat-card--bad {
		background: rgba(239,68,68,0.04);
		border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.12);
	}
	.feat-card--bad:hover {
		border-color: rgba(239,68,68,0.22);
		box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.35), 0 0 0 1px rgba(239,68,68,0.08);
	}
	.feat-card--good {
		background: rgba(34,197,94,0.04);
		border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.12);
	}
	.feat-card--good:hover {
		border-color: rgba(34,197,94,0.22);
		box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.35), 0 0 0 1px rgba(34,197,94,0.08);
	}

	/* Colored left rule */
	.feat-card__rule {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 3px;
		height: 100%;
		border-radius: 0;
	}
	.feat-card__rule--bad  { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #EF4444 0%, rgba(239,68,68,0.2) 100%); }
	.feat-card__rule--good { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #22C55E 0%, rgba(34,197,94,0.2) 100%); }

	/* Ambient corner glow */
	.feat-card--bad::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0; left: 0;
		width: 200px; height: 200px;
		background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 0% 0%, rgba(239,68,68,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
		pointer-events: none;
	}
	.feat-card--good::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0; left: 0;
		width: 200px; height: 200px;
		background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 0% 0%, rgba(34,197,94,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.feat-card__inner {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		padding: 2rem 2rem 2rem 2.5rem;
	}

	/* Header row */
	.feat-card__header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.625rem;
	}

	/* Badge circle */
	.feat-badge {
		width: 26px;
		height: 26px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
	.feat-badge--bad  { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.15);  color: #F87171; border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.25); }
	.feat-badge--good { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.15);  color: #4ADE80; border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.25); }

	/* Label */
	.feat-label {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
	}
	.feat-label--bad  { color: #F87171; }
	.feat-label--good { color: #4ADE80; }

	/* List */
	.feat-list {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.875rem;
		list-style: none;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.feat-item {
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		align-items: flex-start;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: #A1A1AA;
		line-height: 1.55;
	}

	/* Icon circle per item */
	.feat-icon {
		width: 20px;
		height: 20px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-shrink: 0;
		margin-top: 1px;
	}
	.feat-icon--bad  { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.12);  color: #F87171; }
	.feat-icon--good { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.12);  color: #4ADE80; }

	/* Highlight good item text slightly */
	.feat-card--good .feat-item { color: #C4C4CC; }
</style>
